Package org.reroutlab.code.auav.drivers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuavDrivers  
    BatteryDriver
    BatteryDriver connects to DJI and local compute.
    CaptureImageV2Driver
    CaptureImageDriver connects to DJI and local compute.
    DroneGimbalDriver
    DroneGimbalDriver connects to the DJI Gimbal.
    ExternalCommandsDriver
    This driver forwards commands from a network source to any other driver.
    FlyDroneDriver
    FlyDroneDriver connects to the DJI Aircraft instance.
    LocationDriver
    LocationDriver sets, reports and stores the physical location of the AUAV (x,y,z) over time.
    MissionDriver
    This is a Driver Template It exists to facilitate the construction of new Drivers Check the SoftwarePilot Developer Guide for more details at Reroutlab.org/softwarepilot
    PicTraceDriver
    PicTraceDriver pulls images from a directory and labels them as as a corresponding X,Y,Z and T
    URL: coap:\\localhost:port\cr?
    Example: coap:\\127.0.0.1:10452\cr?dc=get-dp=/data/HelloWorld
    Note: all AUAV drivers have resource component "cr" for coap resource
    TemplateDriver
    This is a Driver Template It exists to facilitate the construction of new Drivers Check the SoftwarePilot Developer Guide for more details at Reroutlab.org/softwarepilot
    VisionDriver
    FlyDroneDriver connects to the DJI Aircraft instance.
